         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">23/12/79. ¶  ¶ The last mail, dear Sir William, brought me the enclosed letter ¶  from our venerable friend, Professor DeCaisne, to whom I like to write at an early date in reply. His allusion regardi...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">79.12.23</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To William Macarthur</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">A2939 Macarthur papers, vol. 43, p. 321, Mitchell Library, Sydney.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">23/12/79.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The last mail, dear Sir William, brought me the enclosed letter<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <seg style="">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Letter not found; but see M to J. Decaisne, 20 March 1879 (in this edition as 79-03-20a).</seg>
                  </p>
               </note> from our venerable friend, Professor DeCaisne, to whom I like to write at an early date in reply. His allusion regarding the case of plants sent by him may meanwhile have had its response from you, unless a letter of yours was lost.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">With every reverence</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>your</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: -0.3937in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3937in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
         </div>
